@darionyaphet, If this pull request is related to an existing JIRA issue, it would help us out if you would update the title of this pull request with [STORM-X].  

Here is a [link](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STORM-510?jql=project%20%3D%20STORM%20AND%20resolution%20%3D%20Unresolved%20ORDER%20BY%20priority%20DESC) to some currently unresolved issues in the JIRA system, for reference.

 @atdixon  minor nit pick above. I am trying to test this by running exhibitor, can you provide a sample config for running exhibitor with single host zookeeper. 
I am also concerned about how it will run in secure mode. There is an option to set ACLs https://github.com/Netflix/exhibitor/wiki/Running-Exhibitor but we need to test this as well.
